                     <interp inst="t18180909-221-person1687" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner running, stopped him, and charged him with stealing the time-piece - He denied it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180909-221-person1688">
                  JOHN 
                  HAGGERS
               <interp inst="t18180909-221-person1688" type="surname" value="HAGGERS"></interp>
